Vision operates on the five second rule. 
the more valuable a thing is: [the higher the VALUE]=[the quicker the response to the drop](relative to when/where it drops)
vision algorithm responds to the whole's reaction to the drop.
  vision algorithm recognizes [a drop can be ahead or behind its time] and adjuststs.
vision download is $3.
vision subscription is $3.
vision keeps the download cost.
vision gives the subscription fee to the visionary.
  vision pays each visionary [per like, comment, share, download, record].
  each vision subscription is divided by the viewers actions on the app.
    re-creation - 5pts
    share       - 3pts
    comment     - 2pts
    like        - 1pts

